WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.329 --> 00:00:05.820
Welcome to the market glory tutorial

00:00:05.820 --> 00:00:07.820
at this panel

00:00:07.820 --> 00:00:11.319
you see the bonuses

00:00:11.319 --> 00:00:14.209
and this panel you see the country

00:00:14.209 --> 00:00:17.039
citizens

00:00:17.039 --> 00:00:22.960
and country reserves

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:25.220
at this panel

00:00:25.220 --> 00:00:27.810
you see the government

00:00:27.810 --> 00:00:33.060
the emperor the prime minister and the
normal ministers

00:00:33.060 --> 00:00:36.910
and at the left panel you see the most important part

00:00:36.910 --> 00:00:40.210
let's zoom in

00:00:40.210 --> 00:00:41.330
at first

00:00:41.330 --> 00:00:44.120
you see the inbox and alerts

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:47.240
and alerts are of updates or changes

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:50.820
energy level is the most important
part

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:55.050
you also gain experience by working

00:00:55.050 --> 00:00:56.580
and knowledge

00:00:56.580 --> 00:01:02.540
by buying books on the global or local
market

00:01:02.540 --> 00:01:04.040
if you sum up

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:06.660
all three steps together

00:01:06.660 --> 00:01:09.000
and divide them by three

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:11.940
you will get your productivity

00:01:11.940 --> 00:01:14.680
beneath you can see also

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:20.950
your assets like euros gold and local
currency

00:01:20.950 --> 00:01:26.330
you need at least 10 local currency to get 1 gold piece

00:01:26.330 --> 00:01:31.000
and 4 gold pieces to get 1 euro

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.930
let's first work

00:01:32.930 --> 00:01:36.350
click on work

00:01:36.350 --> 00:01:38.590
than work now

00:01:38.590 --> 00:01:43.750
you need to work three days in a row to
get the work bonus

00:01:43.750 --> 00:01:47.940
and you can work once a day

00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:49.450
let's fight

00:01:49.450 --> 00:01:51.890
click on fight

00:01:51.890 --> 00:01:55.570
attack

00:01:55.570 --> 00:02:00.270
scroll down and click on attack now

00:02:00.270 --> 00:02:04.480
you will see that you always win
against the trainer

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:08.139
you can fight ten times a day

00:02:08.139 --> 00:02:14.089
and each time you fight, you have a 10
minute cool down

00:02:14.089 --> 00:02:17.250
the chat is also and important part

00:02:17.250 --> 00:02:19.309
of this game

00:02:19.309 --> 00:02:24.719
Beneath you can see the chat

00:02:24.719 --> 00:02:28.219
You have the rooms which you can create yourself

00:02:28.219 --> 00:02:29.949
the local chat

00:02:29.949 --> 00:02:34.510
country chat that which you can choose your own country to chat in

00:02:34.510 --> 00:02:36.219
support

00:02:36.219 --> 00:02:37.779
when it's needed

00:02:37.779 --> 00:02:39.309
the trade chat

00:02:39.309 --> 00:02:41.699
and the general chat

00:02:41.699 --> 00:02:44.540
let's click on open

00:02:44.540 --> 00:02:47.379
you can now chat in chat

00:02:47.379 --> 00:02:48.799
and choose

00:02:48.799 --> 00:02:52.349
where you want to chat

00:02:52.349 --> 00:02:57.109
let's go to the forums that's also an
important part

00:02:57.109 --> 00:02:59.639
click on forum

00:02:59.639 --> 00:03:02.949
there you see your local forum

00:03:02.949 --> 00:03:08.819
if you want to look at all other parts
click on the small arrow

00:03:08.819 --> 00:03:09.919
open

00:03:09.919 --> 00:03:12.429
and you will see all the other

00:03:12.429 --> 00:03:14.489
forums of the world

00:03:14.489 --> 00:03:16.579
let's go to the general

00:03:16.579 --> 00:03:18.549
click on general

00:03:18.549 --> 00:03:21.329
here you can ask all your questions

00:03:21.329 --> 00:03:23.019
and find more information. Thank you for watching please like.

